    EventInfoFixed

    Structure representing information about specific ticket (place within room queue).
    ReservationInfo
    Class representing information about single reservation within system.
    Room
    Class representing single room (or other type of attraction) on the event, capable of providing entertainment for visiting groups.
    Room.State
    Enum describing possible states of this room
    RoomInfoFixed
    Class containing immutable information about specific room.
    RoomInfoUpdate
    Class representing mutable information about specific room.
    Sector
    Class representing single sector at given event
    SectorInfoFixed
    Class representing immutable information about specific sector.
    SectorInfoUpdate
    Class representing mutable information about specific sector.
    Server
    Class responsible for running the server, including initialization of database connection, loading event data from database, setting up queue structure and launching client connection listener.
    Server.Task
    Structure representing task given to main server thread, containing all the data necessary to handle the task and respond to requester.
    TourGroup
    Class representing specific event touring group, used as a basic queue system resolution unit.
